---
title: Bang Bang Broccoli with fragrant rice and sweet chilli sauce
description: This crispy baked bang bang  broccoli really lives up to its name. Served with fluffy fragrant rice, charred carrot and rich sweet chilli aioli, this truly is a knock-out dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W14_IE_IECFQVV13673-2_switch_edit_Main_high-e5ce6297.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6462a6330c1e02e39244a0e8.pdf
